<br>
You have the same kind of glowing, rose-colored-glasses view of the old EQ world that an old grandfather has of the world he knew of the past.  The one where girls were girls and men were men, they walked uphill and back from school in the snow because it built character, and everyone knew their place and liked it.<br>
