<br>
EVERYTHING was camped, especially Sol B and Lguk.  In my first incarnation in EQ, I can remember the hordes of people in lguk, crowds sitting at the zone LFG for hours and not a mob up in the place.  It was kind of fun, because it would get to be like a party at the zone, but really, you wanted to be killing something, but everything was camped.<br>
